Three filet working. I need plates.

245
00:17:58,520 --> 00:18:01,120
Fire seven.
Three salade composée up.

246
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:03,120
Don't mess with my mise!

247
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:04,520
Open down low.

