249
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:10,420
Hello, Chef Skinner.
How your night be now?

250
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:12,520
Bonjour, chef.
Hello, Chef Skinner.

251
00:18:12,620 --> 00:18:15,120
- Evening, chef.
